<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-cyber-force> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The National Cyber Force (NCF) is a partnership between defence and intelligence. NCF is part of the Ministry of Defence , the Defence Science and Technology Laboratory , the Secret Intelligence Service , and the Government Communications Headquarters ."@en .
